------------------------------------Post----------------------------------------------
1. Add Employee : Method "Post"
2. URL: http://localhost:9092/loginController/add
3. INPUT: 
   Body -> Raw -> JSON
  
	 {
    "iD": 8,
    "userName" : "rameshs",
     "pass" : "ramesh08"
     }
------------------------------------GET----------------------------------------------
1. Get Employee By Id  : Method "GET"
2. URL: http://localhost:9092/loginController/getEmployee/7

1. Get All Employees : Method "GET"
2. URL: http://localhost:9092/loginController/getEmployees

------------------------------------UPDATE----------------------------------------------

1. Update Customer : Method "PUT"
2. URL: http://localhost:9092/loginController/updateCustomer/8
3. INPUT: 
   Body -> Raw -> JSON
    {
    "iD": 8,
    "userName" : "rameshs",
     "pass" : "ramesh08",
    "email" : "ramesh8gmail.com",
    "firstName":"ram8",
    "lastName": "Kumar6"
   
  }
	
------------------------------------DELETE----------------------------------------------
1. Delete Medicine : Method "DELETE"
2. URL:	http://localhost:9092/loginController/delete/8
	